<paragraph id="6FCDDD0BBE563D70551BA50191B058D4" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
UNITED STATES. New Mexico, 9 km N. of junction of State Highway 152 and Forest Service Road 157, 
<emphasis id="AFB6E3237F29996FD7463C71209D2221" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">K. Keith</emphasis>
